The paper proposes a method for measuring the similarity of second-order semantics in trained models, which is relevant to computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE). The method involves using a neural network to align high-dimensional model parameters, which is a technique commonly used in deep learning (cs.CL).
